source.name: 2006-2010 American Community Survey 5-Year Estimates Summary File
source.description: A nationwide survey that collects information such as age, race, income, commute time to work, home value, veteran status, and other data. Data from the American Community Survey and the Puerto Rico Community Survey were collected during calendar years 2006-2010. Data available for small geographies. Census tract and block group data are available in another dataset.
